  "detailed_description": "Key Features<br><br><strong>\"Perfect Guard\"</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299070/extras/faefea99ca7019e8971a8785c70442e3.poster.avif?t=1736542815\" width=700 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299070/extras/faefea99ca7019e8971a8785c70442e3.webm?t=1736542815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299070/extras/faefea99ca7019e8971a8785c70442e3.mp4?t=1736542815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><u>* \"Perfect Guard\" is the Key Point of combat.</u><br>* A successful \"Perfect Guard\" decreases enemy groggy gauges and restores stamina and divine gauges.<br><br><strong>\"OVE\"</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299070/extras/1684712e690d47bd70ae548f4fdb0264.poster.avif?t=1736542815\" width=700 height=386 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299070/extras/1684712e690d47bd70ae548f4fdb0264.webm?t=1736542815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299070/extras/1684712e690d47bd70ae548f4fdb0264.mp4?t=1736542815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>* \"OVE\" have two types of effect \"power\" and \"Utility\".<br>* \"OVE\" can be obtained through your journey.<br><br><strong>\"Accessory\"</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299070/extras/77409daeafa69bd9dbca9fa6832b7816.poster.avif?t=1736542815\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299070/extras/77409daeafa69bd9dbca9fa6832b7816.webm?t=1736542815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299070/extras/77409daeafa69bd9dbca9fa6832b7816.mp4?t=1736542815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>* \"Accessory ability\" can be purchased from OVE's cradle and mounted in its own inventory.<br><br><br>Elia, a girl of fate sent to free Ella from the tower's control, must overcome many obstacles with the help of OVE. <br><br>Bring down enemies and gather the Nav's trace to grow Elia and equip her with accessories and items for adventure.<br><br>As the game progresses, the enemies you face will have their own characteristics and various gimmicks.<br>Attack your enemies by combining different kinds of OVEs and skills scattered throughout the map.<br><br>Each ability has its own characteristics.<br>Players can change Elia's fighting style by spending the ability points acquired through adventure.<br><br>Start your journey to freedom with Elia, the sword of liberation, overcoming the tough battle against the forces of the tower.",
  "about_the_game": "Key Features<br><br><strong>\"Perfect Guard\"</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299070/extras/faefea99ca7019e8971a8785c70442e3.poster.avif?t=1736542815\" width=700 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299070/extras/faefea99ca7019e8971a8785c70442e3.webm?t=1736542815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299070/extras/faefea99ca7019e8971a8785c70442e3.mp4?t=1736542815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><u>* \"Perfect Guard\" is the Key Point of combat.</u><br>* A successful \"Perfect Guard\" decreases enemy groggy gauges and restores stamina and divine gauges.<br><br><strong>\"OVE\"</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299070/extras/1684712e690d47bd70ae548f4fdb0264.poster.avif?t=1736542815\" width=700 height=386 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299070/extras/1684712e690d47bd70ae548f4fdb0264.webm?t=1736542815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299070/extras/1684712e690d47bd70ae548f4fdb0264.mp4?t=1736542815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>* \"OVE\" have two types of effect \"power\" and \"Utility\".<br>* \"OVE\" can be obtained through your journey.<br><br><strong>\"Accessory\"</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299070/extras/77409daeafa69bd9dbca9fa6832b7816.poster.avif?t=1736542815\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299070/extras/77409daeafa69bd9dbca9fa6832b7816.webm?t=1736542815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299070/extras/77409daeafa69bd9dbca9fa6832b7816.mp4?t=1736542815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>* \"Accessory ability\" can be purchased from OVE's cradle and mounted in its own inventory.<br><br><br>Elia, a girl of fate sent to free Ella from the tower's control, must overcome many obstacles with the help of OVE. <br><br>Bring down enemies and gather the Nav's trace to grow Elia and equip her with accessories and items for adventure.<br><br>As the game progresses, the enemies you face will have their own characteristics and various gimmicks.<br>Attack your enemies by combining different kinds of OVEs and skills scattered throughout the map.<br><br>Each ability has its own characteristics.<br>Players can change Elia's fighting style by spending the ability points acquired through adventure.<br><br>Start your journey to freedom with Elia, the sword of liberation, overcoming the tough battle against the forces of the tower.",
